(v_mod2, 'Why should a listing agent be present for the BPO agent''s property visit?', '["To pressure the BPO agent into a lower value", "To provide comparable sales data and point out property condition issues", "To prevent the BPO agent from entering the property", "It is legally required in all states"]', 1, 2),
(v_mod2, 'What should an agent do if the seller asks for legal advice about their deficiency liability?', '["Give them the best answer they can based on experience", "Tell them not to worry about it", "Refer them to a real estate attorney", "Ignore the question"]', 2, 3),
